# The agent zip lives in the web root only because deploy's FTPS mirror can
# only ship there -- it is NOT meant to be fetchable directly. download.php
# (auth'd) is the only sanctioned way in; this denies the bare URL so the
# binaries aren't world-readable at a guessable path.
#
# Apache 2.4 / LiteSpeed syntax. php -S ignores .htaccess, so local dev serves
# the directory openly -- prod is what this protects.
Require all denied
